<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(٤٦١)</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ أَيضا:</span> <span class="c2">(الرمل)</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>١ - فَمَتَى أَهْلكُ لا أَحْفلُهُ ... بَجَلَ الآنَ مِنَ الْعَيْش بَجَلْ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>٢ - منْ حَيَاةٍ قَدْ مَلِلْنَا طُولَهَا ... وَجَدِيرٌ طُولُ عَيْشٍ أَنْ يُمَلْ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٤٦٢)</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ الْمُستوْغِرُ بنُ رَبِيعَةَ:</span> <span class="c2">(الكامل)</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>١ - وَلَقَدْ سَئِمْت منَ الحَيَاةِ وَطولِهَا ... وَعُمِرْتُ مِن عَدَدِ السنينِ مِئِينَا<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>٢ - مِئَةٌ مَضتْ مِئَتانِ لِي مِنْ بَعْدِهَا ... وَازْدَدْتُ مِنْ عَدَدِ الشُّهُورِ سِنينَا<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٤٦٣)</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ أَكْثَمُ بنُ صَيْفِيٍّ التَّمِيمِيُّ:</span> <span class="c2">(الطويل)</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>١ - وَإِنْ امْرَءًا قَدْ عَاشَ تِسْعِينَ حَجًةً ... إِلَى مِائةٍ لَمْ يَسْأمِ الْعَيش جَاهِلُ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>٢ - مضت مِئَتَانِ غَيْرَ سِتٍّ وَأَرْبَعٍ ... وَذَلِكَ مِنْ عَدِّ الليَالي قَلائِل<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(٤٦٤)</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ ثعلَبَةُ بْن كَعْب الأَوْسِيّ:</span> <span class="c2">(الوافر)</span><a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>١ - لَقَدْ صَاحَبْتُ أقْوَامًا فَأَمْسَوْا ... خُفَاتًا مَا يُجَابُ لَهُمْ دُعَاء<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>